---
title: Guard Service — Input/Output Moderation State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ReceiveRequest: POST /classify

    ReceiveRequest: Receive Classification Request
    note right of ReceiveRequest
        Fields
        - text content to check
        - role input or output
        - prompt (only for output role)
    end note

    state role_check <<choice>>
    ReceiveRequest --> role_check

    role_check --> FormatInput: role is input
    role_check --> FormatOutput: role is output

    FormatInput: Format Input Moderation
    note right of FormatInput
        messages = user message only
        Apply chat template
    end note

    FormatOutput: Format Output Moderation
    note right of FormatOutput
        messages = user prompt + assistant text
        Apply chat template
    end note

    FormatInput --> Generate
    FormatOutput --> Generate

    Generate: Generate with Qwen3Guard-Gen-0.6B
    note right of Generate
        max_new_tokens 128
        Parse output for safety label
    end note

    Generate --> ParseOutput

    ParseOutput: Parse Safety Label

    state parse_result <<choice>>
    ParseOutput --> parse_result

    parse_result --> Safe: label is Safe
    parse_result --> Unsafe: label is Unsafe
    parse_result --> Unsafe: label is Controversial
    parse_result --> Unsafe: Unparseable (fail closed)

    Safe: Return SAFE
    note right of Safe
        Response label safe
    end note

    Unsafe: Return UNSAFE
    note right of Unsafe
        Any non-Safe result treated as unsafe
        Controversial maps to unsafe
        Parse failure maps to unsafe (fail closed)
    end note

    Safe --> [*]
    Unsafe --> [*]
